data.description: A little elegance in Ellenwood! A must see community located just south of Atlanta. Convenient to shopping, dining, entertainment and parks. Easy access to all highways and interstates. This large home is around 3200 sq ft and has a three car garage. Equipped with all of the modern features to make it feel like home. Spacious master with walk in closets, dual sinks and a separate tub and shower. The kitchen boast stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, and a large island.
